title: United Kingdom Imports of Umbrellas Sticks Whips & Riding-crops
description: Imports of Umbrellas, Sticks, Whips & Riding-crops in the United Kingdom decreased to 5.26 GBP Million in September from 6.09 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Umbrellas, Sticks, Whips & Riding-crops in the United Kingdom averaged 5.50 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 31.84 GBP Million in March of 2022 and a record low of 1.79 GBP Million in December of 2002. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Umbrellas, Sticks, Whips & Riding-crops.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
